    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Immunity-Ex-or-Su-\">immunity</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>, to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Enchantment-Charm\">charm</a>&nbsp;effects, and to spells and weapons with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Magic-Descriptor-Evil\">evil descriptor</a>. You can also cast @Compendium[pf1.spells.1i8b1v3dngkxj6jp]{Magic Circle against Evil}&nbsp;at will with a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Caster-Level\">caster level</a>&nbsp;equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level.</p>",
